## DHU (non-negotiables)

- Run from **repository root:** `./android-auto-agents/scripts/dhu-start.sh` or `… auto` — **SDK DHU + USB accessory (`--usb`)**; set **`ANDROID_SERIAL`** when multiple adb devices. The `… adb` subcommand is an **optional** alternate (head unit server); default testing is USB AOA only.
- Do **not** chain `adb … && pkill -x desktop-head-unit && ./android-auto-agents/scripts/dhu-start.sh` — `pkill` can exit `1` and skip the script; use `; pkill … || true;` then the script.

